                                p.lh25 There is #[input(type="text" class="c-input js-escribir")] information  based on  #[input(type="text" class="c-input js-escribir")] conducted by scientists that caused them to reach a #[input(type="text" class="c-input js-escribir")] that people in countries with #[input(type="text" class="c-input js-escribir")] do not have sufficient #[input(type="text" class="c-input js-escribir")] of vitamin D.

                .col.xs12.md6

                    div(class="row col-center mt30")
                        p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Complete the sentence with a word from the table below.
                            .c-cardGreen
                                .c-cardGreenContent.flex.align-items-center.justify-center
